## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources and the complexity of gender roles across different cultures and historical periods. The interpretation of gender roles can vary significantly, and the sources may not cover all perspectives or recent developments in gender studies. Additionally, the data is up to date only until October 2023, and newer insights or studies may not be included.